text: Spinovelleda basilewskyi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1960.BioLib.cz - Spinovelleda basilewskyi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1960
